entries.coal_bin: A large container used for holding solid resources such as coal or ore.
entries.corvette_droid_maint_module: This module is used to regulate the maintenance functions of astromech droids.  It appears to be in working condition.
entries.computer_mainframe: A large computer, used for various purposes.
entries.corvette_bootdisk_4: A bootdisk for the internal systems of a Corellian Corvette class ship.  This one is marked #4.
entries.computer_desktop: A desktop monitor and keyboard, connected to a computer network of some kind.
entries.trash_container: A pile of trash.  There may be something hidden beneath or inside it...
entries.poison_stabilizer: A poison stabilizing agent.  It mixes with toxic fumes to convert them into breathable air.
entries.poison_gas_cloud: A cloud of poisonous or toxic gas.
entries.chemical_reactor: A chemical reactor, putting chemicals in it will change the make up of an experiment.
entries.droid_battery: A Droid Battery, used to recharge pet droids.
